General.Name: Pearl Holdings Acquisition Corp Warrant
General.Description: Pearl Holdings Acquisition Corp focuses on effecting a merger, share exchange, asset acquisition, share purchase, reorganization, or similar business combination with one or more businesses. It focuses on acquiring business in consumer-focused industries, including companies that participate in the lifestyle, technology, healthcare, and wellness sectors. The company was incorporated in 2021 and is based in New York, New York.
